14
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:25,060
Inchcombe realized
his lack of feeling was almost...

15
00:02:25,728 --> 00:02:27,187
Pathological.

16
00:02:28,565 --> 00:02:31,733
"I've been wearing the wrong size
all my life" says Katie.

17
