It's 25 years. A marriage.

41
00:04:08,289 --> 00:04:10,499
Come on, Nicholas.

42
00:04:10,667 --> 00:04:13,085
Or I'm gonna get in a taxi
and find your farm.

43
00:04:13,253 --> 00:04:15,420
No.
Come up there and I'll drag you out.

44
00:04:15,588 --> 00:04:17,756
No, don't.

45
