I thought you'd be pleased.

46
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:23,553
Well, of course I'm pleased.

47
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:28,934
Nadia, go to the pub and stay there.
I'll come when I can.

48
00:04:29,102 --> 00:04:30,602
Are you going to tell her?

49
00:04:30,770 --> 00:04:32,437
Just give me a couple of hours.

50
00:04:33,856 --> 00:04:35,065
Cock pie.

51
00:04:35,733 --> 00:04:38,193
