Good, actually.

52
00:04:38,361 --> 00:04:40,237
Just about to embark on forensics.

53
00:04:40,405 --> 00:04:43,615
Well, give me your pages
and I'll get started.

54
00:04:43,783 --> 00:04:45,909
Reckon I might pack it in
a bit early today.

55
00:04:46,077 --> 00:04:48,161
Need to think about my blood smears.

56
00:04:48,329 --> 00:04:50,872
Might take a drive, have a pint.

57
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,125
Stir the old grey matter up.

58
00:04:53,293 --> 00:04:55,585
Who were you talking to just then?

59
00:04:55,753 --> 00:05:01,216
