should be through in a day or two.

60
00:05:01,384 --> 00:05:03,135
I could come with you.

61
00:05:03,303 --> 00:05:04,845
What?
For a drive.

62
00:05:05,013 --> 00:05:06,722
I don't know when we last went out.

63
00:05:06,889 --> 00:05:09,349
This is absolutely yummy.

64
00:05:09,517 --> 00:05:11,727
Or we could go into Hadditon,
get a meal.

65
00:05:11,894 --> 00:05:13,312
Yes.

66
00:05:14,063 --> 00:05:15,689
But what about the guests?

67
00:05:15,857 --> 00:05:17,190
Mary's got Casey to help.

68
00:05:17,358 --> 00:05:20,068
But I'm supposed to be
thinking, you know, about...

69
00:05:20,236 --> 00:05:23,739
You can run it by me.
I'm good at forensics.

70
00:05:34,834 --> 00:05:37,336
Andy, can I tempt you?

71
00:05:37,962 --> 00:05:40,672
We've got a new academic.
Glen, American.

72
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:42,924
Turns out he's working
on Thomas Hardy.

73
00:05:43,092 --> 00:05:45,469
