some farming questions.

74
00:05:45,636 --> 00:05:48,263
Needs an expert yokel, does he?
Would you mind?

75
00:05:48,431 --> 00:05:50,974
And the... The writers are
eating alfresco tonight.

76
00:05:51,142 --> 00:05:54,311
Could you check there's no
bird shit on the seats? Sorry.

77
00:05:54,812 --> 00:05:55,854
You okay?

78
00:05:57,023 --> 00:05:58,440
Yes.

79
00:05:58,608 --> 00:06:01,276
Nicholas and l
are going out to dinner.

80
00:06:11,287 --> 00:06:12,537
Now.

81
00:06:14,916 --> 00:06:17,125
Fucking bingo.

82
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:31,890
